	<description><![CDATA[You might have already heard that MapR, the leading provider of enterprise-grade Hadoop and friends, is launching its European operations. Guess what? I&#8217;m joining MapR Europe as of January 2013 in the role of Chief Data Engineer EMEA and will support our technical and sales teams throughout Europe. Pretty exciting times ahead! As an aside: &#8230; <a href="http://webofdata.wordpress.com/2013/01/01/mapr-europe-and-me/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a><img alt="" border="0" src="http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=webofdata.wordpress.com&#038;blog=6169642&#038;post=837&#038;subd=webofdata&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />]]></description>
